Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.94,0:00:08.65,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1368,1000)\blur5}sentikinesis
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.94,0:00:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}It is not allowed to hurt others with {\i1}thymia{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.83,0:00:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Every child in our mud whale
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.83,0:00:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}had been taught like this for long.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.14,0:00:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}However,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.57,0:00:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}we made up our minds to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.27,0:00:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}We had been training hard to protect ourselves
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.54,0:00:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}from the attack by the Empire's battleship, Skulax.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.00,0:00:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}But the training was just like some unfamiliar role playing games.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.70,0:00:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Nevertheless, they were the utmost we could do.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.22,0:00:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}And we were really serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.52,0:00:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Thymia does not act directly on human beings.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.56,0:00:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Therefore when we use its power,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.96,0:00:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}we have to focus the forces on bows, arrows and blades.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.02,0:00:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it! Think about the shape of the bow in your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.47,0:00:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Then image if you draw that bow.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.25,0:00:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Also don't forget the arrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.29,0:00:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord0\shad3}I won't forget!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.25,0:00:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Pull the string of the bow.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.03,0:01:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Then look at the mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.51,0:01:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord0\shad3}Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.48,0:01:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot the arrow over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.14,0:01:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord0\shad3}Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.57,0:01:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Even the bows that are too tight for the children,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.24,0:01:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}they can draw with the help of thymia.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.58,0:01:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}It also benefits the accuracy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.17,0:01:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Moving the object itself
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.23,0:01:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}is the basic usage of thymia.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.87,0:01:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.75,0:01:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.92,0:01:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.98,0:01:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.55,0:01:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Dark-natured guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.06,0:01:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Dark-natured baldy!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.90,0:01:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.07,0:01:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Dark-natured record freak destroyer!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.01,0:01:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.01,0:01:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.83,0:01:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Uhh...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.18,0:01:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you guys OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.69,0:01:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your purpose?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.12,0:01:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring them here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.03,0:02:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Your clothes are torn, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.15,0:02:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinono felt sorry and told us to choose some clothes for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.54,0:02:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,This color suits your skin!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.76,0:02:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,This one is also cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.29,0:02:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't fight with them...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.84,0:02:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,May I trim it myself to make it fit me more?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.38,0:02:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.22,0:02:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I will lend you the sewing tools.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.86,0:02:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,My name's Urumi, glad to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.32,0:02:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't stay with those guys, they are not cool at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.96,0:02:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's be together!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.06,0:02:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.47,0:02:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We are also confident with the performance of thymia.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.82,0:02:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.28,0:02:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, tell us more about the enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.91,0:02:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We want to fight together.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.28,0:02:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,...Because our...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.26,0:02:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,...our friends were killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.42,0:02:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Nobody knows whether the route we take is correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.24,0:02:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}But after 4 days, we will face the all-out attack from Skulax.
