Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,==============================================MAIN==================================================
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.38,0:04:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Lasha-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.77,0:04:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We have seldom seen her recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.09,0:04:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But it wasn't that long since she joined the presbytery!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.13,0:04:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It has been... 2 years?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.30,0:04:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But she is already tottering.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.35,0:04:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Assign members of the vigilante group to each team,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.19,0:04:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,to train them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.68,0:05:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And they should act together that day, so each team can be better protected.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.10,0:05:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,How about the members for {\i1}that{\i0} strategy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.55,0:05:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The problem is,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.10,0:05:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,the shirushi loses their power of thymia
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.60,0:05:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,after their mid-20s.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.43,0:05:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We have no choice but make the children to fight...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.17,0:05:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Children...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.74,0:05:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I will try find some people.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.07,0:05:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Lasha-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.09,0:05:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you feel good now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.14,0:05:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing about my feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.99,0:05:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You were training the children, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.66,0:05:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Ye..yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.05,0:05:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The new chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.84,0:05:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard that your younger sister was killed by them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.39,0:05:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You must hate the guys outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.24,0:05:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But you should never forget,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.64,0:05:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,the children may kill somebody tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.83,0:06:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,the children may die tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.92,0:06:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,decided by {\i1}you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.40,0:06:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Lasha-sama,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.84,0:06:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Suo cares about the children more than anyone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.79,0:06:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuchiba,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.66,0:06:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,what about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.69,0:06:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You were together with Taisha,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.58,0:06:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,but you failed to protect her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.86,0:06:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you want a revenge?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.03,0:06:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But you won't fight at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.11,0:06:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The children of shirushi die for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.14,0:06:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuchiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.82,0:06:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's you presbytery's fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.29,0:06:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You only made us to suicide together!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.51,0:06:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have complaints...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.54,0:06:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.62,0:06:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Do whatever you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.66,0:06:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, everything will come to an end soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.84,0:06:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And finally, the cursed children of the whale can be saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.46,0:06:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Lasha-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.68,0:06:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We can only wait for the death if we do nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.86,0:06:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't stop here and wait to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.09,0:07:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oni.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.60,0:07:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You were selected for the strategy of the chief, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.98,0:07:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.50,0:07:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll bring something to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.64,0:07:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiki, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.17,0:07:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oni suddenly appeared in a corner of the residential area someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.21,0:07:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No one knows who is his parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.62,0:07:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And he didn't belong to any team.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.87,0:07:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That guy is always alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.08,0:07:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I think he's name is Oni.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.80,0:07:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,He's weird. Leave him alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.11,0:07:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey dude.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.76,0:07:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll let you be my underling!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.89,0:07:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean let's play together!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.09,0:07:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.82,0:08:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.28,0:08:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You dare!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.35,0:08:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.90,0:08:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.74,0:08:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Both of you violated the rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.02,0:08:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Cuz this guy hit my face.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.68,0:08:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I even bothered to ask him be my underling,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.23,0:08:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,but he's cheeky...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.15,0:08:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to live together in the {\i1}internal{\i0} for a few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.81,0:08:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a chance for you to talk with each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.28,0:08:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn, I hate it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.16,0:08:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.68,0:08:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you want to be out that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.74,0:08:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,They're the same, here and outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.65,0:08:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It can never be the same!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.39,0:08:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't feel bad in such a small place?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.60,0:08:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The island itself is small.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.00,0:08:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We are surrounded by the sand, can't make a single move.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.88,0:08:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,We become adults and die, with ourselves cooped up in the island. 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.05,0:08:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,They're the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.13,0:09:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Then... Then why don't you go out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.04,0:09:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You scum scum scum!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.75,0:09:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of the island if you don't like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.90,0:09:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If you mean you can't go out,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.08,0:09:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll bring you out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.92,0:09:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm, that's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.59,0:09:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I decided!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.39,0:09:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You should be my underling!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.14,0:09:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah no, be my heeler.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.89,0:09:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But, this is also the same...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.11,0:09:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.32,0:09:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Be my {\i1}fellow!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.89,0:09:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll bring you out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.87,0:09:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey you two, get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.74,0:09:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You must hate to be sent to the internal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.80,0:09:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Learn from it, and never...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.70,0:09:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But, it isn't that bad sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.53,0:09:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.23,0:10:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Nibi, what will you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.40,0:10:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.59,0:10:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't given up my dream of going outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.50,0:10:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll knock down every guy on that way,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.92,0:10:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,and bring you out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.14,0:10:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget I was the leader at the beginning!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.71,0:10:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes you were.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.82,0:10:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I still think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.98,0:10:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Cuz I'm one year older than you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.42,0:10:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop laughing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.16,0:10:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It was fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.73,0:10:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.23,0:10:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We can never meet them again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.88,0:10:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.63,0:10:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.88,0:11:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not as iron-minded as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.58,0:11:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You are really amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.03,0:11:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen you cry, for even a single time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.33,0:11:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oni.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.09,0:11:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I... am a bit scaring.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.88,0:11:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know where are you looking at,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.85,0:11:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,and I don't know if you may leave us
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.16,0:11:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and go somewhere yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.47,0:11:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.62,0:11:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me with your eyes on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.02,0:11:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oni!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.54,0:11:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Chakuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.60,0:11:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Lykos.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.89,0:11:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You've changed clothes? It suits you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.80,0:12:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.21,0:12:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.12,0:12:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Because your clothes are worn-out...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.44,0:12:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I sewed it with the old clothes they gave me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.07,0:12:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You did it? For me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.91,0:12:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to wear if you don't like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.61,0:12:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... Lykos?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.80,0:12:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,After all...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.33,0:12:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The minds... are annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.01,0:12:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.54,0:12:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord0\shad3}We are gathering the sand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.22,0:12:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Cuz it's {\i1}Sunamodori{\i0} tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.43,0:12:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We have finished 80% of the barricades on the east side.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.92,0:12:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Although the west side is behind our schedule...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.06,0:12:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Suo?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.80,0:12:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It is impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.97,0:12:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,No,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.29,0:12:54.08,Default,,0,150,0,,{\an3}Sunamodori
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.01,0:12:54.31,Default,,150,0,0,,{\an1}If we assign those who without any works there,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.37,0:12:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The {\i1}Sunamodori{\i0} on the west side...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.83,0:12:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.75,0:12:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,At the moment facing the enemies,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.42,0:13:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,how dare you think about playing with sands!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.58,0:13:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an1}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.15,0:13:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The children should have been looking forward that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.67,0:13:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But it is impossible anyway~
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.52,0:13:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,More importantly, we have an assembly tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.01,0:13:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You must make up our minds in concert.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.28,0:13:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, chief-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.88,0:13:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,...Make sure you understand your position and role,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.23,0:13:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and prepare for anything that may happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.46,0:13:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the tactics for tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.40,0:13:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,There may be something horrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.90,0:13:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,There may be something sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.27,0:13:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But I wish,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.52,0:13:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,through the sky and the sea of sand,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.90,0:13:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,our minds will always connect with each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.44,0:13:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,When you are despaired and frightened,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.20,0:13:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,please remember my wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.81,0:13:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish we shall always be together,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.74,0:13:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,with you and all the livings connected with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.18,0:13:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Suo-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.36,0:14:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Suo-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.31,0:14:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,He has done well this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.02,0:14:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It was splendid!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.01,0:14:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.53,0:14:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.91,0:14:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.59,0:14:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We completed it with over a year, just for this day!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.39,0:14:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a masterpiece of our workshop!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.90,0:14:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Automatic sand-splashing machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.73,0:14:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And the name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.94,0:14:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Automatic! Sand-splashing! Machine!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.12,0:14:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing changed at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.14,0:14:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.23,0:14:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You thought whatever you do, I won't get angry at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.20,0:14:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.41,0:14:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Nezu! Lo! Chakuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.99,0:14:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}He is more angry than we thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.50,0:14:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}No problem,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.61,0:14:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Suo is {\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\1c&H232D3D&}super bad at sports{\3c&H232D3D&\4c&H232D3D&\1c&HFFFFFF&}, we can definitely run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.45,0:14:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.13,0:14:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I did get angry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.15,0:14:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Push it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.68,0:14:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.44,0:14:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Suo-sama has splashed sand!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.25,0:14:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Sunamodori!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.33,0:14:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey... Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.38,0:14:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Suo, stop them!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.46,0:14:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.34,0:14:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Enjoy it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.51,0:14:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}The {\i1}Sunamodori{\i0} is an event held once a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.20,0:14:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}On that day, everybody on the mud whale
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.64,0:15:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}takes part in the battle and splashes sand onto others 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.40,0:15:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}until the sunset.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.06,0:15:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}And there is another meaning for the Sunamodori.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.52,0:15:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}The souls melted in the sand will come back to us
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.58,0:15:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}through the splashed sand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.93,0:15:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Sami...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.44,0:15:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry I'm smiling so soon after you die.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.19,0:15:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But I have never forgotten you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.29,0:15:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I will remember you ever and forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.70,0:15:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Please keep watching me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.12,0:16:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up, Sienna?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.63,0:16:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.32,0:16:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to take part in the battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.92,0:16:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The presbytery has ordered me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.94,0:16:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Please prepare for your suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.36,0:16:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want your dead body to be ugly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.19,0:16:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Does your heart feel nothing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.85,0:16:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.34,0:16:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You cares only about whether the death of your wife is ugly?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.21,0:16:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The feelings of people
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.16,0:16:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,can never be shaped and visible.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.67,0:16:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you cares about the heart
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.56,0:16:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,that nobody really knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.28,0:17:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Neli?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.62,0:17:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness, you are all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.28,0:17:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder after those happened to Fallaina...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.79,0:17:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You are not Neli?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.02,0:17:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.43,0:17:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Neli?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.20,0:17:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl has returned to Mom's tummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.24,0:17:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,To heal Mom's wounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.42,0:17:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.62,0:17:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What is Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.33,0:17:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You can hear my voice clearly?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.05,0:17:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.14,0:17:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't talked with people for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.65,0:17:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Neli and I are twin. We share the same blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.59,0:17:54.82,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1053,1000)}αίμα
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.59,0:17:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Call me Emma.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.61,0:17:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Emma?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.45,0:17:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, Mr. Recording clerk.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.72,0:18:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, promise me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.54,0:18:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha... What? Promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.30,0:18:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Protect the island at any cost.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.78,0:18:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You said you'll protect everybody in the underground.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.79,0:18:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Forever... Let's live together forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.98,0:18:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.42,0:18:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,if you can survive,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.91,0:18:23.44,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1296,1000)}φάλαινα
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.91,0:18:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I will tell you all the secrets of Fallaina!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.00,0:18:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean the history of the mud whale?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.13,0:18:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You know it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.41,0:18:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Emma, who are you and Neli?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.25,0:18:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you trying to tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.02,0:19:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}July 17, 93 S.S.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.55,0:19:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Confirmed a fog caused by the sand dust, before dawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.49,0:19:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}After the sunrise, there was a sandstorm on the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.06,0:19:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}And the visibility was completely obstructed on the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.00,0:19:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We mud whale will intercept the enemies!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.70,0:19:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The most important thing is,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.27,0:19:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,to protect yourselves from the attacks by the enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.37,0:19:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold back the enemies as long as possible, fight them back if possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.45,0:19:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Our goal is to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.47,0:19:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And another thing for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.96,0:19:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,While we are in defense,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.56,0:19:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I ask you to penetrate into the emenies' battleship.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.49,0:19:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And destroy Nous the Skulax inside the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.96,0:19:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Sink their ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.17,0:19:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a very dangerous task.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.25,0:19:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore I only gathered those who with high ability of thymia.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.39,0:20:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,They are the charms I made.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.57,0:20:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,They were used for stuffs like hunting, praying for safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.15,0:20:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway please get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.95,0:20:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Please come back safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.54,0:20:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Suo-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.44,0:20:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Good girl, that's a good reply!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.74,0:20:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.70,0:20:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.10,0:20:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.04,0:20:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.58,0:20:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.96,0:20:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,This is not good. Have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.91,0:20:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the captain of Team 3 of vigilante group. My name is Tokusa.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.62,0:20:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm the captain of this assault team.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.16,0:20:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's cooperate together and respect each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.05,0:20:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oni-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.45,0:20:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Tokusa.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.44,0:20:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say that, Suo-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.72,0:20:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't we friends! Trust me please!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.37,0:20:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.69,0:20:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Lykos,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.99,0:20:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,you are already a member of the mud whale.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.65,0:20:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Care more about yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.87,0:20:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Please be sure to survive and come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.38,0:20:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.23,0:21:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Good girl, a good reply!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.21,0:21:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Chakuro,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.31,0:21:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,since you're the only ones who have seen the Nous...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.38,0:21:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Suo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.73,0:21:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.04,0:21:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Chakuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.03,0:21:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,When you finished the loading,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.25,0:21:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,board on the ship in order and wait for the next instruction!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.68,0:21:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.11,0:21:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Nibi, you are not elected.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.48,0:21:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Remain here and protect Kicha and others.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.18,0:21:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had enough! Don't leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.33,0:21:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Nibi-kun, thank you for your willing but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.91,0:21:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! Don't talk to me, you idiot vigilante!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.35,0:21:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.15,0:21:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, haven't you heard anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.14,0:21:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,There are sounds other than the sandstorm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.46,0:21:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.08,0:22:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,They are coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.53,0:22:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemies, they are right there!
